{
  "stem": "27409.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was called up, because the Romanian army had peasants, many soldiers, but less officers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they took us in order-- we were about 20-odd kilometer from the Polish border.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were sent, with a unit of soldiers, on the border, to stop the avalanche, which was coming from Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because General [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Erich ?] Smigly, the commandant of the Polish forces, they were caught between the German and Russian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they started running to Romania, their whole government, Jews, from Lviv, from another town came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to bring them in a internment camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of them soldiers and Jewish, a lot of Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was Rosh Hashanah time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember, particularly, one family which I stopped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a family, [NON-ENGLISH], I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were from Lviv, a rich store owner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they came, in the-- in their own car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was father, mother, a boy who had-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] there was ick on-- what's, how it's called?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A yellow face all-- Jaundice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jaundice, that is.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a lovely daughter, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't want to send them internment camp and this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I gives them the address of a Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were from-- she was really from Lviv.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so to go there and to let her in towards them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this direction, I give the pass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was control checked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, you didn't think about danger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not officer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was still cadet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had the intelligence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they were peasants, you see?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We That a company.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were 36 soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had a section of the border to control, to check.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But a short time afterwards, we were returned to our studies, more military training.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
